{"title":"玉门二题","authors":["木斧"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":4,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉门二题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木斧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终场的舞台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天铺成的幕布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井塔上挂着一抹鲜艳的纱巾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要来临的黄昏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将携走这匹彩缎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在谢幕的掌声中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井塔也将隐去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晨，在别一个舞台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崭新的朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将挣脱夜的挟持，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再从塔尖上冉冉升起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脊背"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨鲸，饥渴难忍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自远古的泱泱大海游来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口气喝干了海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一晃眼浪迹了几千年……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨鲸卧倒在地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地面上露出了他高昂的头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出了他宽阔粗犷的脊背。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨雷，石破天惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂打着巨鲸的脊背："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还我时间！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还我大海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨鲸激动得浑身发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向四面八方喷出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一浪又一浪的油田！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从脊背的甲骨文中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以读到一个童话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨鲸将要复活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遨游在浩淼的油海！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}